Unloading of a CT Scanner at Policlinico San Donato Milanese with a Bonfiglioli Crane P70000 G
Another operation completed with precision and efficiency! Our Bonfiglioli crane played a key role in unloading a sophisticated CT scanner at the Policlinico San Donato Milanese.
Thanks to the combination of power and millimetric control, we ensured:
Maximum safety: The operation was carried out with care in a highly sensitive healthcare environment.
Absolute precision: The CT scanner was placed perfectly in its designated position.
Timely execution: The work was completed quickly and seamlessly.
Once again, Bonfiglioli cranes prove their reliability in complex and delicate contexts, delivering flawless results.
Bonfiglioli: always ready to tackle the most important challenges.
Credits: autotrasportivioladomenico

Another Successful Operation with Our Crane at the Bank of Italy.
Another remarkable operation completed with precision and professionalism! This time, our crane played a key role in a highly specialized task: loading two transformers at the Bank of Italy headquarters.
Thanks to its extraordinary lifting capacity and utmost reliability, our crane managed the job with total safety, meeting the required timelines and addressing the logistical needs of such a sensitive environment.
Operation Details:
Location: Bank of Italy
Load: Two transformers
Challenge: Millimetric precision and adherence to protocols in a complex operational setting.
Once again, our team and equipment have proven capable of handling even the most unique challenges. 
Bonfiglioli: tailored solutions for every challenge.

Credits fratelliivaldi
